pipeline_summary.name: wait_partition_pipeline
pipeline_summary.description: Comprehensive Pipeline Description: This is a sensor-gated daily ETL pipeline that waits for database partition availability before extracting, transforming, and loading incremental orders data.

components.name: Wait for Partition
components.description: Ensures the daily partition for the orders table exists before starting ETL processing. Uses reschedule mode to free up worker slots during waiting periods.

upstream_policy.description: Waits for the partition to be available

components.name: Extract Incremental Orders
components.description: Extracts new orders data from the daily partition for processing.

upstream_policy.description: Waits for the partition check to succeed

components.name: Transform Orders Data
components.description: Cleans and validates extracted orders data for loading.

upstream_policy.description: Waits for the extraction to succeed

components.name: Load Orders Data
components.description: Loads transformed orders data to the target data warehouse.

upstream_policy.description: Waits for the transformation to succeed
